18:T443,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a titanium-powered mesh fixation device (tacker) for laparoscopic hernia repair. The product family 'PROFOUND N' indicates a non-absorbable fixation system, where 'N' likely denotes 'Non-absorbable'. The 5mm specification refers to shaft diameter, consistent with standard laparoscopic instruments. However, brand is missing and no external verification is available. The device deploys titanium tacks to secure mesh during hernia repair procedures. Classification is internally consistent but requires review due to: (1) missing brand attribution, (2) no external verification sources, (3) inability to confirm if this is a standalone product family or part of a broader PROFOUND platform. The entity is clearly a reusable/single-use applicator device rather than the implantable tack itself, though both are part of the fixation system. Review needed to confirm brand ownership (Meril vs. other manufacturer), verify product nomenclature standards, and determine if 5mm variant should be merged with other shaft sizes under unified family page.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"PROFOUND N - Non-Absorbable Mesh Fixation Device 5mm\",\"description\":\"Titanium powered non-absorbable mesh fixation device for laparoscopic hernia repair\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Hernia Mesh\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 text-sm text-muted-foreground","aria-label":"